USE THESE FILES WITH ALL YOUR OWN RISK.

About:

This script changes databases, tables, and columns charset.
You must set config.php for your server...


Requirements:
php-cli
mysql

Usage:

$ php change.php

Cli script usage:
 
$ php cli.php arg1 arg2 arg3 arg4 arg5 arg6
	 
        arg1: mysql host

        arg2: database name

        arg3: database user name

        arg4: database name

        arg5: character set

        arg6: character collate





        Others:

        --help, help, -h show this text
